Title: Ajax Mine Project
Description: KGHM Ajax Mining Inc. proposes to develop the Ajax Project, a new open-pit copper/ gold mine located south of and adjacent to the City of Kamloops. The mine would have a production capacity of up to 24 million tonnes of ore per year, over an anticipated 23-year mine life.

Title: Emergency Program Act
Description: Feedback is invited on 12 topics arising from the Emergency Program Act. You can provide feedback by joining the online discussion or sending your comments by email. The opportunity for comment is open from Jan. 11, 2016, until Apr. 22, 2016 at 4 p.m.
PublicEventDescription: The online discussion sets out challenges in the current legislation as well as proposals for possible changes.
